    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Engineered for the purist, this E92 M3 centers around the S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, utilizing individual throttle bodies to achieve instantaneous throttle response and an 8,400 RPM redline. The M-DCT dual-clutch gearbox facilitates lightning-fast shifts, working in tandem with the M Variable Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. This chassis remains tight, with the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing adaptable suspension kinematics. Comprehensive maintenance has been performed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, securing the longevity of the high-strung internals. A mechanically sound specimen of BMW's final naturally aspirated M-car that delivers peak atmospheric performance.",
